&lt;h1 id="keynes-on-the-currency"&gt;Keynes on the Currency&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Feb 26 2008&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There is no subtler, surer means of overturning the existing basis of society than to debauch the currency. The process engages all the hidden forces of economic law on the side of destruction, and it does it in a manner which not one man in a million is able to diagnose.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Perpetual Stimulation Machine</title><link>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/orig/perpetual-stimulation-machine/</link><pubDate>Sat, 16 Feb 2008 21:51:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/orig/perpetual-stimulation-machine/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/person/naval/zh/perpetual-stimulation-machine.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
